                     <interp inst="t18400511-1397-offence-1" type="offenceSubcategory" value="simpleLarceny"></interp> for stealing, on the 2nd of May, 3 sovereigns and 2 half-sovereigns, the monies of <persName id="t18400511-name-497" type="victimName">
